OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777227067
OL,3,CMotorway closed after crash involving
OL,4,Ccoach
OL,6,FA section of the M4 has been closed
OL,7,Ffollowing a crash involving a car and
OL,8,Fa coach overnight.
OL,10,FWiltshire Police were called to the
OL,11,Fwestbound carriageway between
OL,12,Fjunctions 14 ( Hungerford) and 15 (
OL,13,FSwindon East) at around 3am on Sunday,
OL,14,FApril 26th.
OL,16,FIt's reported the crash involved a
OL,17,Fwhite BMW and a National Express
OL,18,Fcoach. Emergency services have not yet
OL,19,Freleased reports of any injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
