OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777227067
OL,3,CMotorway closed after crash involving
OL,4,Ccoach
OL,6,FMotorists were stuck in the closure
OL,7,Ffor around three hours before being
OL,8,Fturned around and taken off at
OL,9,Fjunction 14.
OL,11,FPolice say the road is likely to be
OL,12,Fclosed until the afternoon and are
OL,13,Furging drivers to find alternative
OL,14,Froutes.
